beverly hills cop ii is a 1987 american action comedy film directed by tony scott , written by larry ferguson and warren skaaren and starring eddie murphy .   it is the sequel to the 1984 film beverly hills cop and the second installment in the beverly hills cop series .   murphy returns as detroit police detective axel foley , who reunites with beverly hills detectives billy rosewood ( judge reinhold ) and john taggart ( john ashton ) to stop a robbery/gun-running gang after captain andrew bogomil ( ronny cox ) is shot and seriously wounded .   although it made less money than the first film and received mixed reviews from critics , the film was still a box office success , making $ 153.7 million domestically .   aside from box office success , the film was nominated for an academy award and for a golden globe award for best original song , for bob seger 's " shakedown " .